'rank-math',1]],'The featured image should be at least 200 by 200 pixels to be picked up by Facebook and other social media sites.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'SEO Settings for Search Page'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Edit SEO settings for the search results page'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Current Step'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Current Step Data'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Page %1$d of %2$d'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'LLMS Txt'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Serve a custom llms.txt file to guide AI models with posts, terms, and most important content on your website.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'React Settings UI'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Enable the new React-powered interface for the plugin settings. Disable to revert to the classic PHP-based settings page.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Off'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Media'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Enable Tracking'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Products tagged &ldquo;%s&rdquo;'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'New!'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Content AI %s'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'AI Tools'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Content AI Tools'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Content Editor'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Content AI Editor'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Chat'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Content AI Chat'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Content AI History'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Review analytics and sitemaps'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Site Tagline'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Your theme may display the Site Tagline, and it can also be used in SEO titles &amp; descriptions. Set it to something unique. You can change it by navigating to <a href="%s">Settings &gt; General</a>.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Most WordPress themes place your site\'s tagline in a prominent position (inside header tags near the top of the page).  Using the right tagline can give your site an SEO boost.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Unfortunately, the standard WordPress tagline is "Just Another WordPress site."  That\'s pretty sloppy looking, and it does nothing for your SEO.  In fact, it\'s actually a security risk - it makes it easy for hackers with a WordPress exploit to locate your site with an automated search.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Changing your tagline is very easy.  Just head on over to <a target="_blank" href="%1$s">Settings - General</a> in WordPress\'s admin menu (on the left), or click on the link in this sentence.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The tagline is the second option.  Choose a tagline that summarizes your site in a few words.  The tagline is also a good place to use your main keyword.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Confirm custom tagline is set for your site'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Blog Public'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Your site may not be visible to search engine.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'You must %1$sgo to your Reading Settings%2$s and uncheck the box for Search Engine Visibility.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Check your site\'s visibility to search engines'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Permalink Structure'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'For the best SEO results, use a custom permalink structure, preferably one that includes the post title (<code>%%postname%%</code>). You can change it by navigating to <a href="%s">Settings &gt; Permalinks</a>'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The standard permalink structure is pretty ugly - WordPress generates offputting URLs like: http://www.yoursite.com/?p=99'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'It\'s not very kind on the eyes, and it does nothing for your site\'s SEO.  In fact, it can hurt it - Google\'s bot is quite cautious about crawling pages that look auto-generated.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Fortunately, it\'s very easy to fix.  Just hop on over to <a target="_blank" href="%1$s">Settings - Permalinks</a>.  Then chose the "Post Name" option.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'This option will replace the "?p=99" part of the URL with the post\'s title, like this: http://www.yoursite.com/my-amazing-post-title/'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'This looks nice for readers - and it gets your keywords into the URL (keywords in the URL is a ranking factor).'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Check your site for SEO-friendly permalink structure'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Setting focus keywords for your posts allows Rank Math to analyse the content.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Rank Math allows you to set a focus keyword for every post and page you write - the option is in the "Meta Box", which appears under the text editor in the screen where you write and edit content.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Rank Math uses these focus keywords to analyze your on-page content.  It can tell if you\'ve done a good job of optimizing your text to rank for these keywords.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Of course, if you don\'t give Rank Math a focus keyword to work with, it can\'t give you any useful feedback.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Fixing this issue is easy - just edit the post, and set a Focus Keyword.  Then follow Rank Math\'s analysis to improve your rankings.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Confirm focus keywords are set for all your posts'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Post Titles Missing Focus Keywords'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Make sure the focus keywords you set for the posts appear in their titles.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'HTML Page Titles play a large role in Google\'s ranking algorithm.  When you add a Focus Keyword to a post or page, Rank Math will check to see that you used the keyword in the title.  If it finds any posts or pages that are missing the keyword in the title, it will tell you here.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Fixing the issue is simple - just edit the post/page and add the focus keyword(s) to the title.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Verify the presence of focus keywords in your post titles'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Search Console'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Register at Google Search Console and verificate your site by adding the code to <a href="%1$s">Settings &gt; Verificate Tools</a>, then navigate to <a href="%2$s">Settings &gt; Search Console</a> to authenticate and link your site.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Google\'s Search Console is a vital source of information concerning your rankings and click-through rates.  Rank Math can import this data, so you don\'t have to log into your Google account to get the data you need.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'You can integrate the Google Search Console with Rank math in the <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">Search Console tab</a>. of Rank Math\'s General Settings menu.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Read <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">this article</a> for detailed instructions on setting up your Google Webmaster account and getting Rank Math to work with the Google Search Console.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Confirm if Rank Math is connected to Search Console'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Sitemaps'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'XML sitemaps are a special type of text file that tells search engines about the structure of your site. They\'re a list of all the resources (pages and files) you would like the search engine to index. You can assign different priorities, so certain pages will be crawled first. Before XML sitemaps, search engines were limited to indexing the content they could find by following links. That\'s still an important feature for search engine spiders, but XML sitemaps have made it easier for content creators and search engines to collaborate.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'If you don\'t have an XML sitemap, the best option is to install a plugin that creates sitemaps for you. That way you\'ll know the sitemap will always be up-to-date. Plugins can also automatically ping the search engines when the XML file is updated. The Rank Math WordPress plugin gives you complete control over your site\'s XML sitemaps. You can control the settings for each page as you write or edit it, and Rank Math will ping Google as soon as you submit your edits. This results in fast crawls and indexing.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Check the presence of sitemaps on your website'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Automatic Updates'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Enable automatic updates to ensure you are always using the latest version of Rank Math.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Verify auto-updates are enabled for Rank Math'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Edit llms.txt'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Configure your llms.txt file for custom crawling/indexing rules.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The keyword to be researched.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The country for which the keyword should be researched.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The ID of the post initiating the keyword research request.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'If true, forces a fresh research request.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The content of the new post.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The title of the new post.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'An array of AI-generated and existing outputs to be saved.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The API endpoint for which the output was generated.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Indicates if the request was for the Chat endpoint.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The parameters used to generate the AI output.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Credit usage details returned by the API.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Indicates if the request to delete the output was for the Chat endpoint.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The output index to delete, applicable only to the Chat endpoint.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The selected prompt to be updated in the recent prompts.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'The prompt data to be saved in the database.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'A list of prompts received from the API to be saved in the database.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Content AI plan to update in the Database.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Content AI reset date to update in the Database'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'List of attachment IDs for which to generate alt text.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Post ID.'=>['urls'=>[],'names'=>[],'cmp'=>['rank-math',1]],'Post Type.'=>['urls'=>[],'nam